    {
      "id": "mnshpiv5xzktbtfjd4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 568,
      "y": 60,
      "strokeColor": "#e8590c",
      "text": "GET /.well-known/openid-configuration\n→ discover JWKS URI → fetch public key",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-10T05:53:21.091Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-04-10T05:53:21.091Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mnshpiv51lmtcymtwpxi",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 568,
      "y": 198,
      "strokeColor": "#868e96",
      "text": "fetched on startup, then cached",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-10T05:53:21.091Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-04-10T05:53:21.091Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mnshpiv5elqv7yf0qft",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 50,
      "y": 240,
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "text": "1. On startup, Spring fetches the JWKS (public key) from Keycloak's well-known endpoint",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-10T05:53:21.091Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-04-10T05:53:21.091Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mnshpiv581zdqrbslng",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 50,
      "y": 260,
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "text": "2. Frontend sends requests with a signed JWT in the Authorization header",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-10T05:53:21.091Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-04-10T05:53:21.091Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mnshpiv585qgft9ti4h",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 50,
      "y": 280,
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "text": "3. NimbusJwtDecoder validates the JWT signature against the cached public key",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-10T05:53:21.091Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-04-10T05:53:21.091Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "callout",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 50,
      "y": 310,
      "width": 840,
      "height": 35,
